BROOK CROMPTON -- SMALL CAP GEMI've been following this company over the past 10 years  and seen its transformation from a left-for-dead  debt ridden corpse to now a vibrant  growing cash generative machine. It was founded in 1947 and previously known as Lindeteves-Jacoberg Limited (LJL). The current name change took place in May 2015 after the entryWoolong Holding Group Limited as controlling shareholder.Wolong was founded in 1984 and is a giant in the world of electric motors & drives. They currently have more than 18 000 employees  total assets of USD4.9 billion  and annual sales of USD5.6 billion. The Woolong group have production bases all over the world and a state-level enterprise technology center. It is a leading enterprise in the global motor industry with excellent competitiveness and service capabilities.They saw in the old-LJL a top-tier management team with key distribution relationships in established industrial markets in the United Kingdom  Middle East  North Africa  Continental Europe  North America  and the Asia-Pacific markets.The Group's trademark Brook Crompton is a well-established brand name that has been in the market for more than 40 years. Brook Crompton is a leading provider of electric motors for the global industrial market  offering products that are deployed in sectors ranging from marine  mining and oil & gas to HVAC (heating  ventilation  air conditioning).The listco changed its name to"Brook Crompton Holdings Ltd."with effect from 04 May 2015 to heighten public awareness of the brand name at the holding company level  project the image of the Group’s global reach  as well as to align the Group’s brand identity as the sole distributor of the Brook Crompton brand of motors.The synergy with Wolong is useful to Brook Crompton on both the sales channel and the production side. On the production side  Wolong has invested in production for the traditional “made in Europe” Brook Crompton W series product by building production units in China  and in Vietnam (not affected by the same level of import duties as China).
